Title: Performance: Monotony + The One Electronic
Book Description: 'Monotony is powered by two game boys running LSDJ- resulting in an assault of grungy- hyperactive- progressive- chiptune dance music. The One Electronic is an electronic artist who specializes in using vintage video game consoles to produce super lo-fi dance music- bringing you a fusion of retro video game sound with modern day EDM flair. Featuring live visuals by Ohhinaifu and Walk In Circles.'
